ObservationValueConceptSearchParameter

Parameter value-date:date

Searches for an observation whose value is a date by the specified date range. eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Observation?value-date={date}

ResourceObservation
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesObservation
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
